Author: baur <baurzhansahariev@gmail.com>
Date:   Mon Nov 18 10:31:58 2024 +0100

    Normalize geometry collection geo shapes provided as object literals
    
    Transform geometry collection to MultiPoint or MultiPoligon if possible.
    This alignes it with WKT string behavior

